====Noun====
'''booby'''  (''plural''  '''boobies''')
# Any of various [[tropical]] [[seabird]]s from the genera ''[[Sula]]'' and ''[[Papasula]]'', resembling [[gannet]]s; [[rest]]s at [[night]] in the [[rigging]] of [[sailing]] [[ship]]s from where it is easy to [[catch]]
